query:
SELECT e.id, e.tipoEvento, e.dataEvento, e.dataEventoFim, e.turmaId, t.codigo 
FROM eventos e 
JOIN turmas t ON e.turmaId = t.id 
WHERE t.codigo = '902' 
ORDER BY e.dataEvento DESC
LIMIT 10;
